Commentary Text: Navdeep Saini to N Jagadeesan, out N Jagadeesan Run Out!! Excellent from Morris! But what was Jagadeesan doing there? He probably gave up midway. This was a full toss that was toe-ended to mid-off and they looked to pinch the single. Must say that it was there to be taken but Morris was swift to the ball and fires in a direct hit at the bowler's end. Jagadeesan was way short. Commentary Text: Washington Sundar to du Plessis, out Caught by Chris Morris!! RCB have been on point playing the dimensions in Dubai, and we see that again.
